description:
Kate and Doree respond to an email from a listener who feels behind in life at 30 and wants a career change. Then they discuss some steps to take when depression hits and your typical self-care isn’t cutting it, and get a listener recommendation for cozy mystery reads. Also, they ponder an intricate "thought experiment" from a listener that answers the very important question: What makeup would you want to have after being rescued off a desert island? 

To leave a voicemail for a future mini-ep, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.

Theme music by Riot.


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
